<p>Tendrils batter all <a href="/wiki/Creature" title="Creature">creatures</a> within 10 feet of you. They must make a <a href="/wiki/Ability_Scores" title="Ability Scores">Strength</a> save. On a fail, a target takes 2d6 <a href="/wiki/Damage_Type" title="Damage Type">necrotic</a> damage and can't take <a href="/wiki/Order_of_Combat#Reactions" title="Order of Combat">reactions</a> until its next turn. On a success, it takes half damage and suffers no other effects.
</p><p><b>At Higher Levels:</b> The damage increases by 1d6 for each slot level above 1st.
</p>
